Market Analysis and Insights:

Global Purpose-Built Backup Appliance Market

Purpose-built backup appliance market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 15.0% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on purpose-built backup appliance market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth.

A standalone device used for disk-based storage purposes is a purpose-built backup appliance. In addition, these systems provide data recovery applications in the integrated infrastructure that initiates data transfer and automatic data restoration and backup.

Increasing awareness and focus of enterprises on data protection and recovery infrastructure, rising growth of the internet of things market, increasing adoption of stringent rules and regulations about data protection and data security, growing popularity of software-based appliances in various industry sectors, easy access, easy deployment, and single point of contact are some of the major as well as important factors which will likely to accelerate the growth of the purpose-built backup appliance market in the projected timeframe of 2021-2028. On the other hand, rising preference towards cloud storage, increasing need for data analytics along with increasing technological advancements in backup appliances in storage-based industries which will further contribute by generating immense opportunities that will lead to the growth of the purpose-built backup appliance market in the projected timeframe mentioned above.

High cost associated with storage and backup technology along with easy availability of cost effective substitutes which will likely to act as market restraints factor for the growth of the purpose-built backup appliance in the above mentioned projected timeframe. Cyber-security concerns will become the biggest and foremost challenge for the growth of the market.

